# Exploration: cp

## Rounds
  round 0: 40 isolated cumulative, 10 identical in round (discovery)
  round 1: 49 isolated cumulative, 16 identical in round (refinement)
  round 2: 53 isolated cumulative, 22 identical in round (refinement)
  round 3: 58 isolated cumulative, 29 identical in round (refinement)

## Observed: 34/36 flags
  20 solo, 14 via combination
  2 additional error-differentiated
  1 behavioral aliases detected

Aliases: -L = --dereference, -P = --no-dereference, -S = --suffix, -T = --no-target-directory, -a = --archive, -f = --force, -i = --interactive, -l = --link, -n = --no-clobber, -s = --symbolic-link, -t = --target-directory, -v = --verbose, -x = --one-file-system

## Solo (unique behavior)
